{"mode": "market_intel", "engine": "cerebras-120b", "insight": "**Actionable Insight:**

Identify and resolve the issue of **"Data Drift" in AI Models**, where models become less accurate over time due to changes in the underlying data distribution.

**Concrete Approach:** Develop a simple, automated **"Data Drift Detector"** tool that uses a combination of statistical methods and ML models to monitor and alert users when a model's performance degrades due to data drift. This tool can be integrated with existing model deployment pipelines and alert users via Telegram or email notifications.", "run": 815}
